HAVOK - APATHY ESPLANADE EP 2008



The latest release from the tech-death metallers from Sweden! This six-track EP was released early February 2008 and has already reached great acclaim within the metal community. Their previous record, WORLD SHROUD, was amongst other things entitled &quot;Best in Sweden&quot; by Close-Up Magazine. Their sound has been compared to a mix of Decapitated, Gojira and Hate Eternal.

According to Masterful Magazine, if you&amp;#039;re looking for something more adventurous - this is something for you. (http://www.masterful-magazine.com/review_result.php?wynik=detail&amp;rodzaj=recenzje&amp;id=2074)

Swedish magazine Slavestate claims that they do not want to hear any more demos from Havok - if they don&amp;#039;t get signed soon Slavestate will loose faith in the music industry. (http://www.slavestate.se/?e=196)

